description: Tech Trivia is a trivia game that will test your knowledge on tech subjects! Just ask Alexa to open Tech Trivia and start a new game. Then you'll be presented with a few questions about different technology subjects. Just say the number of the answer you pick and see if you get it right!
name: Tech Trivia
shortDescription: Tech Trivia is a trivia game that tests your knowledge on technology subjects. Questions on different companies, products, events, and people.
